node.text:
Today’s the day for the return of the @inspiration4 mission! The deorbit burn starts at 6:16 pm ET (22:16 UTC) and the landing just offshore Cape Canaveral comes 50 minutes later (23:06 UTC). This is will only be the third time Crew Dragon has landed with people and the first time a capsule splashdowns on the Atlantic Ocean since the Apollo program! Credit @spacex
.
.
Check out our Crew Dragon merch! Link in bio!
